snippet.title: Triangle Congruence Statement - How to Write (Geometry)
snippet.description:
Learn how to write a triangle congruence statement in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.  We go through three examples discussing techniques for matching up corresponding angles and sides.

0:23 Example 1 Showing the Triangles are Congruent by SAS and Writing the Congruence Statement.
2:49 Example 2 Showing the Triangles are Congruent by ASA and Writing the Congruence Statement
3:58 Example 3 Showing the Triangles are Congruent by AAS and Writing the Congruence Statement
5:00 Other Way to Write the Triangle Congruence Statement
